Whether you're trying to keep up with the Jones's, or impress the new neighbor on the block, look no further than the Cypress Spruce Tree.Â 

The Cypress Spruce Christmas tree has a power-pole construction. A power-pole is where each tree section has built-in wiring that effortlessly connects the lighting strands as you set up your tree. You'll experience a seamless set-up to light your tree up without having to connect any wires. All of our pre-lit Christmas trees are skillfully hand-strung to camouflage the appearance of wires.

There are 8 light settings that are controlled with a remote or the foot pedal. 1.Warm white steady 2. Multi-color steady 3. Warm white slow flash 4. Multi-color slow flash 5. Warm white and multi-color exchange slow flash 6. Warm white fast flash 7. Multi-color fast flash 8. Warm white and multi-color exchange fast flash. Sizes 6.5ft to 10ft.
